entries.femaleVariant: Nobody goes north! Not even the Wraiths!
No, come on...! I was just joking!
What in the...?! Stop that this instant! Do you want him getting sick from all those fumes?
Oh yeah? I bet you won't venture out to the oil fields. Only real, brave nomads go there.
No, I'm not! I'm not afraid of anything!
Chicken, huh? I know you're too chicken.
